.type-panel-content
  %p.hint
    Code analysis questions show a syntax-highlighted code block plus either ruled answer lines or multiple-choice options. Author via the
    %code POST /api/questions/bulk
    API or a seed file. Use the JSON options shape:
  %pre.hint-json
    :plain
      {
        "language": "python",
        "code": "def foo():\n    pass",
        "answer_format": "lines"
      }
  %p.hint
    For multiple choice, set
    %code "answer_format": "multiple_choice"
    with a
    %code choices
    array where each item is
    %code { "text": "...", "correct": true|false }
    \.
